    <legis-type>A BILL</legis-type>
    <official-title>To provide that the only health plans that the Federal
		  Government may make available to the President, Vice President, Members of
		  Congress, and Federal employees are those created under the Patient Protection
		  and Affordable Care Act or offered through a health insurance
		  exchange.</official-title>
